channel.title: Plz help!
channel.description: Ok, I downloaded "death scape" source off of Xbox Modder's list. When I go to extract the files, a thing comes up saying the file is password protected. What do I do? Is there a way around the password? And most of the files I can not open without a certain program(theres at least 50) and they all take separate programs, is there a way I can get through that with out downloading 50 different programs?

item.title: Plz help!
item.dc:creator: @jehanne jehanne
item.description:
@jehanne wrote:

most of the files are .rar files, just download winrar.

and when a source is pw protected, ask the pw, or just throw the file away u cant do anything with it
